1. *Smeo* si to da mi kažeš ranije. (You could have told me that earlier.)
2. Ja *smem* da radim ovaj posao. (I am allowed to do this job.)
3. *Smeš* li da mi pozajmiš novac? (Would you be willing to lend me money?)
4. *Sme* li se pušiti ovde? (Is smoking allowed here?)
5. On *nije smeo* da ode kući bez dozvole. (He wasn't allowed to go home without permission.)
6. *Nismo smeli* da propustimo taj sastanak. (We couldn't afford to miss that meeting.)
7. *Smeo bih* da tvrdim da je ovo najbolji restoran u gradu. (I dare say this is the best restaurant in town.)
8. *Smejala se* glasno dok je gledala komediju. (She laughed out loud while watching the comedy.)
9. *Ne smeš* da ostaviš otvorena vrata. (You must not leave the door open.)
10. *Smeli su* da pređu reku pre nego što je postalo previše duboko. (They dared to cross the river before it became too deep.)